Package com.microsoft.azure.management.website.models Description

This package contains the model classes for WebSiteManagementClient. Use these APIs to manage Azure Websites resources through the Azure Resource Manager. All task operations conform to the HTTP/1.1 protocol specification and each operation returns an x-ms-request-id header that can be used to obtain information about the request. You must make sure that requests made to these resources are secure. For more information, see Authenticating Azure Resource Manager requests..
